36
00:04:24.180 --> 00:04:26.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>No matter how busy we are,</i>

37
00:04:26.683 --> 00:04:31.020 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>on this one day, we meet up in this room…</i>

38
00:04:33.523 --> 00:04:35.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>carrying the same pain inside.</i>

39
00:04:41.072 --> 00:04:43.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ah, that’s enough for me.

40
00:04:44.409 --> 00:04:47.662 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
