including your height.

47
00:05:07.098 --> 00:05:08.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Shut up!

48
00:05:08.725 --> 00:05:09.892 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Nobu.

49
