56
00:05:30.872 --> 00:05:32.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
&lrm;YUMEKO

57
00:05:32.582 --> 00:05:33.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yumeko-chan!

58
