-Super view!

83
00:07:53.973 --> 00:07:55.975 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
If we can see them from the room,

84
00:07:56.058 --> 00:07:58.019 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I guess there was no need
for the disguises.

85
00:07:58.102 --> 00:07:59.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah.

86
00:07:59.479 --> 00:08:02.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hey! Where’s Hachiko? Why isn’t she here?

87
00:08:02.231 --> 00:08:05.109 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
