and told her not to come.

88
00:08:05.193 --> 00:08:09.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Nah. That guy’s not one to fuss over
something like going to see fireworks.

89
00:08:09.530 --> 00:08:13.242 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
