No news is proof that she’s safe.

90
00:08:13.326 --> 00:08:14.869 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No, it’s proof that something’s wrong!

91
00:08:40.228 --> 00:08:44.482 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I have to get going. Everyone’s waiting.</i>

92
00:08:45.316 --> 00:08:51.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
