<i>I will be a traitor for sure this time.</i>

93
00:08:53.658 --> 00:08:56.911 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But I can’t stop crying.</i>

94
00:08:56.994 --> 00:08:58.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bye.

95
00:09:00.748 --> 00:09:04.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I thought I’d feel better</i>
<i>once we talked things over.</i>

96
00:09:04.210 --> 00:09:06.379 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But now I realize that</i>

97
00:09:06.462 --> 00:09:10.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I felt the most comfortable</i>
<i>when I was with Shoji.</i>

98
00:09:12.051 --> 00:09:15.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>We were good friends before we went out.</i>

99
00:09:15.763 --> 00:09:17.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I thought that</i>
<i>once the break-up drama died down,</i>

100
00:09:17.765 --> 00:09:20.601 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>things could go back</i>
<i>to the way they used to be.</i>

101
00:09:23.896 --> 00:09:28.025 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>But now I’ve really lost him forever.</i>

102
00:09:29.151 --> 00:09:32.989 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I should’ve treasured him more back then.</i>

103
00:09:43.541 --> 00:09:44.959 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
SHIN

104
00:09:46.419 --> 00:09:48.170 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What should I do?</i>

105
00:09:48.254 --> 00:09:49.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>If I see Nobu now,</i>

106
00:09:49.422 --> 00:09:52.300 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
