<i>and act normal.</i>

107
00:09:52.383 --> 00:09:55.344 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>I’ll get sad and start crying</i>
<i>all over again.</i>

108
00:09:56.053 --> 00:09:58.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Those with a record</i>
<i>must refrain, you know.</i>

109
00:09:59.640 --> 00:10:01.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>What should I do?</i>

110
00:10:03.185 --> 00:10:07.148 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>But I don’t ever wanna betray them</i>
<i>again without saying anything.</i>

111
00:10:08.149 --> 00:10:11.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>If I can’t go,</i>
<i>then I have to tell them that.</i>

112
00:10:15.865 --> 00:10:18.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Hello, Hachiko?</i>

113
00:10:21.078 --> 00:10:22.330 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Nana?</i>

114
00:10:23.581 --> 00:10:24.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>Where are you?</i>

115
00:10:25.458 --> 00:10:27.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Near Jackson’s.

116
00:10:27.835 --> 00:10:31.339 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
