<i>The fireworks have already started.</i>

117
00:10:34.550 --> 00:10:38.971 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I’m sorry. I don’t think… I can go…

118
00:10:40.598 --> 00:10:42.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why not?

119
00:10:44.143 --> 00:10:48.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Hey, why are you crying?</i>
<i>Is something wrong?</i>

120
00:10:51.025 --> 00:10:51.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>I’m so…</i>

121
00:10:53.361 --> 00:10:56.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
scared of… seeing Nobu.

122
00:11:13.297 --> 00:11:17.343 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It’s all right. Nobu isn’t here.

123
00:11:26.685 --> 00:11:29.980 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You know, that guy has no guts.

124
00:11:30.064 --> 00:11:34.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
