What a chicken.

125
00:11:35.736 --> 00:11:38.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>So you’ve got nothing to worry about.</i>
<i>Hurry on over.</i>

126
00:11:39.031 --> 00:11:41.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Shin and Yasu are really</i>
<i>looking forward to seeing you!</i>

127
00:11:43.119 --> 00:11:45.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>Don’t be so cold by telling us</i>
<i>you can’t come now.</i>

128
00:11:46.956 --> 00:11:51.377 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
