129
00:11:54.463 --> 00:11:55.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Okay.

130
00:12:05.766 --> 00:12:07.101 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
