to how you want them to be!

136
00:12:21.824 --> 00:12:25.744 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
No, I just know what it’s like
to be so scared

137
00:12:25.828 --> 00:12:29.081 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
